This is a full-time, on-site role for a Shop Manager located in Bengaluru. The Shop Manager will be responsible for managing daily operations, overseeing store management, and delivering exceptional customer service and experience. Key tasks include staff management, maintaining inventory, ensuring a high standard of cleanliness and hygiene, and driving sales and profitability.

 Qualifications
 
Excellent Communication skills to interact effectively with staff and customers
Operations Management and Store Management skills for ensuring smooth daily operations
Strong Customer Service and Customer Experience skills to provide high satisfaction
Experience in retail or food and beverage industry is a plus
Proven ability to manage and motivate a team
Flexible and adaptable to store needs
